2000", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC3013.html", target="_top", tooltip="The purpose of this document is to express what the engineering community as represented by the IETF expects of Internet Service Providers (ISPs) with respect to security.  This document specifies an Internet Best Current Practices for the Internet Community, and requests discussion and suggestions for improvements."];
